title: CCK Podcast: Happy Birthday Barstool (featuring Trent & Francis)
description:
It's Barstool's 17th anniversary! Trent has THOUSANDS of people muted on Twitter. Francis calls in to discuss Megan Thee Stallion getting shot. How early can you remember? Brad Pitt's New gf and the NBA boycott.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
